{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/python-Function-Parameters","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"0220dc0b-30f8-5501-ada4-df9e353e30ad","html":"<h1 id=\"function-parameters\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#function-parameters\" aria-label=\"function parameters permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Function Parameters</h1>\n<h3 id=\"1-positional-arguments\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-positional-arguments\" aria-label=\"1 positional arguments permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. positional arguments</h3>\n<p>함수에 parameter가 순서대로 전해지는 경우</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nfunction<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 6</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>위의 예제에서 x가 non-default value parameter, y는 값을 할당했기 때문에 default value parameter 이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-keyword-arguments\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-keyword-arguments\" aria-label=\"2 keyword arguments permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Keyword Arguments</h3>\n<p>parameter 이름으로 맞추어서 값을 전해주는 경우</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-interpolation\"><span class=\"token string\">f'</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">+</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> \n\nfunction<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'love'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># love+4</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>parameter 순서가 바뀌어도 에러가 발생하지 않음</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-mixing-positional-arguments-and-keyword-arguments\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-mixing-positional-arguments-and-keyword-arguments\" aria-label=\"3 mixing positional arguments and keyword arguments permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Mixing positional arguments and keyword arguments</h3>\n<p>순서를 맞추어서 parameter 값을 전해주는 positional arguments와 keyword arguments를 혼용하여 사용하는것도 가능\n(혼용시에도 인자 순서대로 할당해야 한다.)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-interpolation\"><span class=\"token string\">f'</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\"> and </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nfunction<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 3 and 4</span>\nfunction<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>y<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># SyntaxError: positional argument follows keyword argument</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>keyword argument가 positional argument 보다 더 앞으로 위치되어 함수가 호출되어서 에러 발생</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"4-parameter-default-value\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-parameter-default-value\" aria-label=\"4 parameter default value permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. Parameter Default Value</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'love'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-interpolation\"><span class=\"token string\">f'</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">+</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> \n\nfunction<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#love+3</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>(주의)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'peach'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-interpolation\"><span class=\"token string\">f'</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">+</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># SyntaxError: non-default argument follows default argument</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>default 값이 정의된 parameter가 default 값이 정의 되지 않은 parameter 보다 앞에 위치해 있기 때문에 에러 발생</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"인자의-우선순위\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%EC%9E%90%EC%9D%98-%EC%9A%B0%EC%84%A0%EC%88%9C%EC%9C%84\" aria-label=\"인자의 우선순위 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>인자의 우선순위</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>positional arguments(함수에 parameter가 순서대로 전해지는 경우)</li>\n<li>default arguments</li>\n<li>positional arguments들의 집합</li>\n<li>keyword arguments (함수 호출시 값을 지정)</li>\n<li>keyword default arguments (keyword arguments에 default 값이 지정된 경우)</li>\n<li>keyword arguments의 집합</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"함수를-정의-할-때-default-value-parameter를-non-default-value-parameter-앞에-정의-하면-왜-안되는지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98%EB%A5%BC-%EC%A0%95%EC%9D%98-%ED%95%A0-%EB%95%8C-default-value-parameter%EB%A5%BC-non-default-value-parameter-%EC%95%9E%EC%97%90-%EC%A0%95%EC%9D%98-%ED%95%98%EB%A9%B4-%EC%99%9C-%EC%95%88%EB%90%98%EB%8A%94%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"함수를 정의 할 때 default value parameter를 non default value parameter 앞에 정의 하면 왜 안되는지 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>함수를 정의 할 때 default value parameter를 non-default value parameter 앞에 정의 하면 왜 안되는지?</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>매개변수에 값을 전달할 때는 위치를 기준으로 하기 때문에, 앞에 있는 파라미터에 기본값을 지정했다면 뒤에 있는 변수에도 기본값을 지정해주어야 한다.</li>\n<li>함수를 호출할 때 값을 하나만 전달한다면, 어떤 매개변수를 생략한 것인지 알 수 없기 때문이다.</li>\n<li>파이썬에서는 이런 함수의 정의를 허용하지 않아서 위와 같은 SyntaxError를 발생시킨다.</li>\n</ol>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/python-Function-Parameters","tagSlugs":["/tag/python/","/tag/function-parameters/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-03-28","description":"python Function Parameters","tags":["python","Function Parameters"],"title":"Function Parameters","socialImage":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/python-Function-Parameters"}}}